	"packageName": "@anvilkit/validator",
	"readme": [
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": "# @anvilkit/validator\n\nExport-readiness validation for Puck component configs and AI-generated output.\n\n> **Alpha status (0.1.x).** Both "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`validateComponentConfig`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " and "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`validateAiOutput`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " are implemented and tested.\n\n## Install\n\n"
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "```bash\npnpm add @anvilkit/validator @puckeditor/core\n```"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": "\n\n## Quickstart\n\n### Validating a Puck component config\n\n"
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "```ts\nimport { validateComponentConfig } from \"@anvilkit/validator\";\n\nconst result = validateComponentConfig(puckConfig);\nif (!result.valid) {\n  console.error(\"Config issues:\", result.issues);\n}\n```"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": "\n\n### Validating LLM-generated PageIR\n\n"
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "```ts\nimport { validateAiOutput } from \"@anvilkit/validator\";\n\nconst result = validateAiOutput(llmResponse, availableComponents);\nif (!result.valid) {\n  // Do NOT dispatch to Puck — surface issues back to the AI retry loop.\n  console.error(\"AI output rejected:\", result.issues);\n}\n```"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": "\n\n## Phase 3 references\n\nSee the [Phase 3 plan]("
		},
		{
			"kind": "relative-link",
			"text": "../../docs/plans/phase-3-export-ai-pipeline-plan.md",
			"target": 2
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ")\n("
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`M3 — @anvilkit/validator`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ") and the\n[architecture package catalog]("
		},
		{
			"kind": "relative-link",
			"text": "../../docs/ai-context/anvilkit-architecture.md",
			"target": 3
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ")\n("
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`§7 — @anvilkit/validator [Planned]`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ") for the validator's trust\nboundary and dependency rules.\n\n## Error Codes — "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`validateComponentConfig`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": "\n\n| Code | Level | Description |\n|------|-------|-------------|\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`E_MISSING_RENDER`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " | error | "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`component.render`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " is not a function |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`E_MISSING_FIELDS`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " | error | "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`component.fields`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " is not an object |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`E_NON_SERIALIZABLE_DEFAULT`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " | error | A default prop value fails JSON serialization |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`E_FIELD_SHAPE_INVALID`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " | error | A field does not match the Puck Field union |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`E_ASYNC_RENDER`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " | error | "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`component.render`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " is an async function (Puck does not support async render) |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`W_MISSING_DESCRIPTION`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " | warning | "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`component.metadata?.description`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " is empty or undefined |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`W_UNKNOWN_FIELD_TYPE`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " | warning | Field type is not one of the 10 AiFieldType cases |\n\n### Why "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`E_ASYNC_RENDER`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " is a hard failure\n\nPuck renders components synchronously during its reconciliation loop. An async render function silently breaks — it returns a Promise object instead of React elements, which Puck coerces to "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`[object Promise]`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " or a blank node. This is impossible to debug from the editor, so we fail hard at validation time.\n\n## Issue Codes — "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`validateAiOutput`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": "\n\nCodes are embedded as a "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`[CODE]`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " prefix in each "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`AiValidationIssue.message`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ". Callers (notably the AI copilot retry loop in Phase 4) switch on them.\n\n| Code | Severity | Description |\n|------|----------|-------------|\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`INVALID_STRUCTURE`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " | error | Response is not an object, missing "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`root`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ", or "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`type`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " is not a string |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`UNSUPPORTED_VERSION`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " | error | "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`PageIR.version`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " is not "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`\"1\"`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`UNKNOWN_COMPONENT`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " | error | Node "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`type`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " is not in "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`availableComponents`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " (may include a closest-match suggestion) |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`MISSING_REQUIRED_FIELD`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " | error | A required field is absent from "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`node.props`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`INVALID_FIELD_TYPE`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " | error | A field value does not match the declared "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`AiFieldType`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`INVALID_ENUM_VALUE`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " | error | A "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`select`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " field received a value outside the declared options |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`INVALID_ASSET`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " | error | An entry in "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`PageIR.assets`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " is malformed (bad "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`kind`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ", missing "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`url`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ", etc.) |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`MAX_DEPTH_EXCEEDED`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " | error | Node tree exceeds the hard cap of 16 levels (DoS guard) |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`UNKNOWN_FIELD`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " | warn | A prop is not declared in the component's "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`AiComponentSchema.fields`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " |\n\n### Trust boundary\n\n"
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`validateAiOutput`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " is the only thing standing between untrusted LLM output and "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`puckApi.dispatch`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ". If "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`result.valid === false`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ", the caller MUST NOT apply the response. Per architecture §9, validation failure surfaces immediately; retry logic is Phase 4.\n\n## Dependency contract\n\n| Allowed | Forbidden |\n|---------|-----------|\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`@anvilkit/schema`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " (runtime) | "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`@anvilkit/ir`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": ", React, plugins |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`@anvilkit/utils`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " (runtime) | |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`zod`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " (runtime) | |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`@anvilkit/core`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " (types-only) | |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`@puckeditor/core`"
		},
		{
			"kind": "text",
			"text": " (peer, types-only) | |\n\n## Peer dependencies\n\n| Package | Version |\n| ------- | ------- |\n| "
		},
		{
			"kind": "code",
			"text": "`@puckeditor/core`"
		},
		{
